snippet.title: Hello Engineer - Out Now on Google Stadia! (Early Access)
snippet.description:
https://stadia.com/link/jAjWHgQUhFbwQCyYA
Hello Engineer is now available for Early Access, play it first on Google Stadia! 

Hello Engineer is a multiplayer machinery-building construction game set in the Hello Neighbor universe. Scavenge, craft, and overcome challenges in the sandbox world of the mysterious Golden Apple amusement park, originally built by Mr. Peterson himself.

#HelloEngineer #HelloNeighbor
